        <li>Does not close or modify open positions</li>
        <li>Does not provide trading signals or directional advice</li>
        <li>Does not transmit your trade data to any external service</li>
        <li>Does not require broker credentials</li>
        <li>Does not guarantee that revenge trading will not occur — it raises the structural cost of acting on the impulse</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Platform requirement</h2>
