        Meridian is a NinjaTrader 8 add-on for Windows only. It operates within NinjaTrader's execution environment
        and cannot monitor trading activity on other platforms or through browser-based interfaces. If you trade
        exclusively through NinjaTrader 8, the behavioral monitoring covers your full session.
      </p>

